						               													<description>If you prefer bagna caoda to bland aperitif nibbles and you've always thought that the farmers of the Granda (the province of Cuneo) knew a lot about food, this is the game for your foodie soul.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Merenda sinoira is a quick and simple card game that brings with it a long culinary knowledge to have fun with friends and family and rediscover the traditional recipes of the Granda.&amp;#10;Take advantage of your innate talents and combine the best wine to enhance the flavors and outperform the competition.&amp;#10;Taste the simplicity of tradition!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game lasts about half an hour, so you can take another round right away.&amp;#10;Shuffle the 110 illustrated playing cards and collect the right cards to compose the &amp;quot;battuta al coltello&amp;quot;, the &amp;quot;vitello tonnato&amp;quot; and many other dishes. Play at home and match the best wine.&amp;#10;The aim of this game of cards and recipes is to get the highest score by combining the ingredient cards to get the best dishes. Match them with drinks to get more points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
